<h2 id="cascader"><a class="header-anchor" href="#cascader" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Cascader</h2>
<p>If the options have a clear hierarchical structure, Cascader can be used to view and select them.</p>
<h3 id="basic-usage"><a class="header-anchor" href="#basic-usage" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Basic usage</h3>
<p>There are two ways to expand child option items.</p>
